snippet: Andy Murray's renewed partnership with Ivan Lendl got off to a winning start on Sunday and the Briton said the American coach was impressed with his battling qualities as he rallied to lift the Queen's Club trophy for a record fifth time....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray's renewed partnership with Ivan Lendl got off to a winning start on Sunday and the Briton said the American coach was impressed with his battling qualities as he rallied to lift the Queen's Club trophy for a record fifth time.

headline.print_headline: Murray Impresses Lendl With Fighting Spirit at Queen's
headline.main: Murray Impresses Lendl With Fighting Spirit at Queen's
